sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant KBD as Keyboard
    participant CP as CommandPalette
    participant IDX as CommandIndex
    participant Router as Router
    participant EM as EngineManager
    participant API as TauriAPI

    User->>KBD: Press Ctrl+K / Cmd+K
    KBD->>CP: keydown listener fires
    CP->>CP: createOverlay() — render overlay DOM
    CP->>CP: input.focus()
    CP->>IDX: searchCommands('') — empty query returns all
    IDX-->>CP: CommandItem[]
    CP->>CP: renderResults(items)

    User->>CP: Types "hermes"
    CP->>IDX: searchCommands('hermes')
    IDX-->>CP: [engine:switch:hermes, nav:chat (via keyword)]
    CP->>CP: renderResults(filtered) — highlight matches

    User->>CP: Press Enter or Click item
    CP->>CP: overlay.remove() — close palette
    CP->>IDX: command.execute()

    alt Navigation command
        IDX->>Router: navigate('/chat')
        Router-->>Router: loadRoute() → render page
    else Engine switch command
        IDX->>EM: switchEngine('hermes')
        EM-->>API: persist engine choice
        API-->>EM: ok
        EM-->>Router: navigate(defaultRoute)
    else Action command (restart gateway)
        IDX->>API: restartService('ai.openclaw.gateway')
        API-->>IDX: ok
        IDX->>CP: toast('Gateway restarting', 'success')
    end

    User->>KBD: Press Escape
    KBD->>CP: keydown Escape
    CP->>CP: overlay.remove()
